                  "id": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pz51r7d/manifest/annotation/p1",
                  "type": "Annotation",
                  "motivation": "commenting",
                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Rev. I. Leeser</addressee>\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>\n                    <hi rend=\"underline\">South Fourth Street 118</hi>\n                </placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"align(right)\"><placeName>New York</placeName>, <date>January 29<hi rend=\"sup\"\n                        >th</hi> 1847</date></p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Dear friend:</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">With the same mail, you will<lb/> get a sermon which I delivered on\n                    <add>שבת חנוכה</add><lb/> to the Jewish congregation in <date>August</date>\n                <add><placeName>Augusta</placeName></add>? And which<lb/> my brother translated. If\n                you like it you<lb/> may print it in your Occident.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">I will send you other papers<lb/> too and I wish you would let me\n                know<lb/> how much you want to pay, without<lb/> considering my person. I will give\n                the<lb/> amount to the welfare and I <add>gladly</add> leave <del>it</del><lb/>\n                <del>to you how much you want to give.</del><lb/> the amount of money up to you.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Did you not get an answer<lb/> yet from\n                    <placeName>Claiborne</placeName>? I am a little<lb/> short on money and could\n                use the<lb/> balance very well.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Awaiting your reply, I am</p>\n            <p>as ever your friend <persName role=\"author\">D. Lilienthal</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3pz51r7d/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
